# Normalize line endings: store everything as LF in the repo, regardless of the
# committer's OS. Without this, Windows core.autocrlf leaves CRLF in the working
# tree while the repo stores LF, producing phantom Prettier/format failures that
# don't reproduce on Linux CI.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets: never normalize or diff as text.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.docx binary
